Japanese title: Hunter x Hunter (2011)
Episode: 107
Episode length: 25 min
Anime type: TV Series
Air date: 04 December 2013
Description: A remake of the original series with different staff and cast. Gon is a youth who lives on Kujira Isle. His dream is to become a Hunter like his father, to search out lost treasures, artefacts, and mythical creatures. Determined to become a professional Hunter willing to stake his life in challenging the unknown, he sets off on a journey and meets fellow Hunter wannabes Killua, Kurapika, and Leorio. ~ translated and adapted from official site by Cranston
